data.comment: The match has started at Borås Arena.
Norrkoping's Sead Haksabanovic gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 1, It's a goal kick for the home team in Boras.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a Norrkoping throw-in in Elfsborg's half.
Jeppe Okkels for Elfsborg drives towards goal at Borås Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
In the minute 3, Throw-in for Elfsborg in the half of Norrkoping.
Goal kick for Norrkoping at Borås Arena.
Elfsborg pushes forward through Rami Kaib, whose finish on goal is saved.
In the minute 5, In Boras a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Norrkoping to take a throw-in in Elfsborg territory.
Can Norrkoping get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Elfsborg's half?
In the minute 6, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Elfsborg's Rasmus Alm is on target but unsuccessful.
In the minute 9, Elfsborg have a goal kick.
Can Norrkoping capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
Goal! Sead Haksabanovic gives Norrkoping a 0-1 lead.
In the minute 11, That's a fine assist from Isak Bergmann Johanneson.
Ball goes out of play for a Norrkoping goal kick.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards Norrkoping a goal kick.
In the minute 14, Ball safe as Elfsborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Elfsborg are in shooting range from this free kick.
In the minute 16, Elfsborg push forward at Borås Arena and Rasmus Alm gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Norrkoping defence.
Linus Wahlqvist (Norrkoping) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
Jonathan Levi for Norrkoping gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
In the minute 18, It's a goal kick for the home team in Boras.
Goal kick for Elfsborg at Borås Arena.
Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 21, Ball goes out of play for a Elfsborg goal kick.
Elfsborg are pushing forward but Per Frick's finish is wide of the goal.
Norrkoping have a goal kick.
In the minute 23, Throw-in Norrkoping.
Goal! Elfsborg go level at 1-1 through Simon Olsson in Boras.
Great play from Rasmus Alm to set up the goal.
In the minute 26, In Boras Elfsborg drive forward through Simon Olsson. His shot is on target but it's saved.
It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Norrkoping close to the penalty box.
Norrkoping surge into the attack at Borås Arena but Linus Wahlqvist’s header is off-target.
In the minute 27, Mohammed Al-Hakim awards Elfsborg a goal kick.
Can Elfsborg get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Norrkoping's half?
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 30, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a Elfsborg throw-in in Norrkoping's half.
Elfsborg advance rapidly upfield but Mohammed Al-Hakim blows for offside.
Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
In the minute 32, Norrkoping awarded a free kick in their own half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards Elfsborg a goal kick.
Eric Smith of Norrkoping smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
In the minute 35, Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
Norrkoping's Jonathan Levi breaks free at Borås Arena. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Goal kick for Elfsborg at Borås Arena.
In the minute 36, Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Free kick for Norrkoping in the half of Elfsborg.
Ball goes out of play for a Elfsborg goal kick.
In the minute 38, Norrkoping have a goal kick.
Free kick Elfsborg.
Johan Larsson (Elfsborg) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
In the minute 39, It's a goal kick for the away team in Boras.
Norrkoping are whistled for offside.
Elfsborg to take a throw-in in Norrkoping territory.
In the minute 41, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Norrkoping in their own half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Norrkoping.
Corner awarded to Norrkoping.
In the minute 44, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Norrkoping.
Joseph Okumu is booked for the home team.
The first-half has come to a close in Boras.
In the minute 46, The second-half is underway in Boras.
Norrkoping awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Ishaq Abdulrazak is on a sub for Egzon Binaku for Norrkoping.
In the minute 48, Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
Elfsborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Isak Bergmann Johanneson (Norrkoping) gets a yellow card.
In the minute 50, Throw-in for Elfsborg in the half of Norrkoping.
In Boras, Elfsborg push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Boras.
In the minute 55, Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Elfsborg attack but Joseph Okumu's header doesn't find the target.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards Norrkoping a goal kick.
In the minute 56, Important block from the Norrkoping defence as Jeppe Okkels fires in a strike for Elfsborg.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Norrkoping in their own half.
Throw-in for Elfsborg at Borås Arena.
In the minute 58, Elfsborg have a goal kick.
In Boras Elfsborg attack through Jeppe Okkels. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Norrkoping at Borås Arena.
In the minute 59, Ball goes out of play for a Norrkoping goal kick.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Boras.
Throw-in for Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 61, Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the away team a throw-in.
Free kick for Norrkoping in the half of Elfsborg.
Free kick Elfsborg.
In the minute 62, Elfsborg are coming forward and Johan Larsson gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
Goal kick for Norrkoping at Borås Arena.
Free kick for Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 64, Ball safe as Elfsborg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Johan Larsson gets his shot on target but fails to score for Elfsborg.
Play has been temporarily suspended for attention to Sead Haksabanovic for Norrkoping who is writhing in pain on the pitch.
In the minute 66, Elfsborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Sead Haksabanovic has recovered and rejoins the match in Boras.
Norrkoping will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Elfsborg.
In the minute 67, Elfsborg's Simon Olsson gets in a shot on goal at Borås Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Throw-in Elfsborg.
Throw-in for Norrkoping at Borås Arena.
In the minute 68, Penalty! Mohammed Al-Hakim points to the spot, great chance for Elfsborg...
Henrik Castegren (Norrkoping) has received a first yellow card.
Per Frick nets and Elfsborg now lead 2-1. The goal came from the penalty spot.
In the minute 70, Throw-in for Elfsborg in their own half.
Simon Thern (Norrkoping) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Elfsborg drives forward and Johan Larsson gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In the minute 73, Corner awarded to Elfsborg.
Elfsborg's Frederik Holst misses with an attempt on goal.
Ball goes out of play for a Norrkoping goal kick.
In the minute 75, Norrkoping awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Elfsborg in their own half.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 78, Norrkoping to take a throw-in in Elfsborg territory.
Throw-in for Norrkoping in the half of Elfsborg.
Can Norrkoping get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Elfsborg's half?
In the minute 79, Kevin Alvarez is replacing Eric Smith for the away team.
Free kick in a good position for Norrkoping!
Jonathan Levi for Norrkoping gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
In the minute 81, Mohammed Al-Hakim awards Elfsborg a goal kick.
Elfsborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
In Boras a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 84, Norrkoping's Henrik Castegren attacks the ball with his head but his effort fails to hit the target.
Elfsborg have a goal kick.
In Boras a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 86, Elfsborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Free kick for Norrkoping in the half of Elfsborg.
Rasmus Alm (Elfsborg) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 87, Henrik Castegren of Norrkoping gets in a strike, but is off target.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Boras.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Norrkoping in their own half.
In the minute 88, Free kick for Elfsborg in their own half.
In Boras Norrkoping attack through Sead Haksabanovic. The finish is off target, however.
Ball goes out of play for a Elfsborg goal kick.
Jeppe Okkels (Elfsborg) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Mohammed Al-Hakim will wait an extra 2 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 2nd half.
Corner awarded to Elfsborg.
Elfsborg's Rami Kaib gets in a shot on goal at Borås Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Norrkoping's Jonathan Levi gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Elfsborg have a goal kick.
The match is over. Final score 2-1.
